headline: Lam Research Introduces the Semiconductor Industry's First Collaborative Robot for Fab Maintenance Optimization
summary: Lam Research Corp. (Nasdaq: LRCX) today introduced Dextro™, the semiconductor industry's first collaborative robot (cobot) designed to optimize critical maintenance tasks on wafer fabrication equipment. Now deployed in multiple advanced wafer fabs around the world, Dextro enables accurate, high-precision maintenance to minimize tool downtime and production variability. It drives significant first-time-right (FTR) results that can enhance yield.
